Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biela lopta. Piata cena.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyhrávate balík vreckoviek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale, ale...
