Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:12.45,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}habatake yo kibou no sora he
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:12.66,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}letí až do neba, kde ešte existuje nádej.
